title: MOTIVATIONAL SPEECH #2: Limitations Are Optional
itunes:title: MOTIVATIONAL SPEECH #2: Limitations Are Optional
description:
Episode 382 - This is a short motivational speech that I made for you to listen to every day, if you want to do so. The only limits that exist in your life are the ones that you place on yourself or the ones that others have placed on you that you have accepted. Break through those limitations and create something special in your life!
